Got some questions?

Why should I subscribe to freshbox if I only want some bananas evey week? It's an amazingly better deal. Each box is full of fresh and nutrious fruits and veggies straight from your local farmers. You don't need to solve a math puzzle to figure this is a better deal. Do I always get amazing fruits and veggies? It's up to you. Some people love greens and veggies, while others are in love with fruits. Whatever your taste is, we deliver fresh of what you want each week. How often does this fresh happiness box show up next to my door? You tell us how often you want it. Most of our customers subscribed to weekly freshbox. You can do weekly, biweekly or every other day. You decide ☺. Why shouldn't I just buy these at grocery store? Fresh from farm > fresh from grocery store. Get it? Also, have you ever noticed the package of produce at a store is bigger than actual product. Unless you are into fancy packaging and half fresh produce, we don't see why you shouldn't buy from us. Free delivery, amazing deal - so what's the catch? There isn't one. Seriously. We minimize our costs by using little to no packaging, cut middlemen between you and farmers and use amazing technology. How about cancellation fees or some hidden fees? No cancellation fees, no hidden fees and no fees at all, except what you pay for your fresh produce. We hate fees as much as you do, if not more. You are saying cancel/pause anytime, but how do I do it? Simple. Mike is your private assistant. Simply text like "Skip this week", "Pause my plan" etc. We made it so simple even kids can do it. No more going around different dashboards and finding the buttons. You're welcome.
); }
